      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUNTER (7) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the minors last time when third (35.33) at this track making it back to back placings. Has never missed the frame at the trip from three starts. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Capable of going well again. WEST ON MENACE (8) missed the frame last time after colliding with another runner in a Novice race at this track, finishing a 9 length fifth (35.60). Better than last start and can bounce back. RED HOT BONNIE (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Hum Bug Monelli (35.14) in a Novice race. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Hard to beat again. SPEED CHELLER (1) is worth consideration.",
